    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《战术脉冲》是一款拥有集高度拟真丰富战术、多样化武器装备和动态呼吸系统制于一体的第一人称拟真射击游戏，采用虚幻5引擎精心打造，以其惊人的画面表现力、逼真的物理效果以及高度互动的环境使玩家将沉浸于一个充满紧张刺激与战略深度的战场世界，在这里，智慧与勇气并重，战术与射击交织，等你来挑战！《战术脉冲》都将为你带来前所未有的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139610/extras/b0624e8191067c4db3056f738f09920e.avif?t=1771297981\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139610/extras_big/b0624e8191067c4db3056f738f09920e.avif?t=1771297981 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139610/extras/7cc55118a809bf33462b7ebce3526998.avif?t=1771297981\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139610/extras_big/7cc55118a809bf33462b7ebce3526998.avif?t=1771297981 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
